Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:22.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果心终会消失不再
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:38.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:51.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:54.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:59.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:05.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:12.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:16.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:22.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:28.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:34.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
