Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}せめて声の限り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:38.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}慟哭と絶望を歌いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}僕らを待つ運命は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:51.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}何れもただ命が夢を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:54.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}駆け抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:59.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今の続き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:05.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}君が泣いた夜はその中に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:12.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}遠い未来の輝きを隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:16.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静けさが君を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:22.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まぶしい丘 きっと行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:28.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}君の地平へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:34.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Ring your bell
